PN,30801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784765892
OL,3,CWeight loss drugs like Mounjaro
OL,4,C'linked to hair loss', researchers say
OL,6,FWeight loss and diabetes drugs such as
OL,7,FMounjaro, Ozempic and Wegovy are
OL,8,Flinked to an increased risk of hair
OL,9,Floss, researchers have said.
OL,11,FPeople taking GLP-1 stimulant drugs
OL,12,Fhave reported hair loss to regulators,
OL,13,Fbut a new study involving around
OL,14,F50,000 people appears to strengthen
OL,15,Fthe link.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784765892
OL,3,CWeight loss drugs like Mounjaro
OL,4,C'linked to hair loss', researchers say
OL,6,FResearchers used electronic patient
OL,7,Fdata from the University of
OL,8,FPennsylvania Health System to compare
OL,9,Frates of alopecia, a form of hair
OL,10,Floss, in adults using GLP-1 drugs to
OL,11,Fmanage diabetes with those taking
OL,12,Fother medications.
OL,14,FThe team noted that regulators in the
OL,15,FUS had already received reports
OL,16,Flinking the drugs to hair loss,
OL,17,Fparticularly semaglutide (Wegovy and
OL,18,FOzempic) and tirzepatide (Mounjaro).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784765892
OL,3,CWeight loss drugs like Mounjaro
OL,4,C'linked to hair loss', researchers say
OL,6,FSo far in 2026, the UK Medicines and
OL,7,FHealthcare products Regulatory Agency
OL,8,F(MHRA) has received 399 reports of
OL,9,Fhair loss linked to tirzepatide,
OL,10,Ffollowing 541 reports last year.
OL,12,FIt has also received 148 reports of
OL,13,Fhair loss associated with semaglutide,
OL,14,Falongside 164 reports last year.
OL,16,FFor the new study, researchers
OL,17,Fexamined people with Type 2 diabetes
OL,18,Ftaking GLP-1 receptor stimulants and
OL,19,Fcompared them with patients using
OL,20,Fother diabetes drugs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784765892
OL,3,CWeight loss drugs like Mounjaro
OL,4,C'linked to hair loss', researchers say
OL,6,FAfter adjusting for factors that could
OL,7,Faffect the results, including age and
OL,8,Fweight, researchers found GLP-1 use
OL,9,Fwas associated with a 37% higher risk
OL,10,Fof alopecia compared with one of the
OL,11,Fother types of drugs, SGLT-2 inhibitors
OL,13,FGLP-1 drugs were also linked to a 68%
OL,14,Fhigher risk of hair loss compared with
OL,15,Fanother type, known as DPP-4
OL,16,Finhibitors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784765892
OL,3,CWeight loss drugs like Mounjaro
OL,4,C'linked to hair loss', researchers say
OL,6,FFurther analysis suggested the
OL,7,Fassociation was linked to non-scarring
OL,8,Falopecia, where hair follicles remain
OL,9,Fintact, and hair has the potential to
OL,10,Fregrow.
OL,12,FThe researchers, including from the
OL,13,FUniversity of Pennsylvania in the US,
OL,14,Fwrote in the British Medical Journal
OL,15,F(BMJ) that case reports and analyses
OL,16,Fof the US Food and Drug Administration
OL,17,F(FDA)'s Adverse Event Reporting System
OL,18,Fdescribe "occurrences of hair loss".
OL,26,@zD@JOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
