OL,3,CWeight loss drugs like Mounjaro
OL,4,C'linked to hair loss', researchers say
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThey single out semaglutide (Wegovy
OL,12,Fand Ozempic) and tirzepatide
OL,13,F(Mounjaro) as being particularly
OL,14,Fhigher risk, and say the FDA has
OL,15,F"indicated that it is evaluating this
OL,16,Fpotential safety signal".
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
