FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784765892
OL,3,CWeight loss drugs like Mounjaro
OL,4,C'linked to hair loss', researchers say
OL,6,F"Although hair loss does not typically
OL,7,Fresult in physical harm, it may have
OL,8,Fsignificant psychosocial consequences,
OL,9,Faffecting self-esteem, quality of
OL,10,Flife, and adherence to treatment,"
OL,11,Fresearchers add.
OL,13,FOn the reasons why people may suffer
OL,14,Fhair loss while on the drugs, the team
OL,15,Fsaid the "most likely mechanism"
OL,16,Frelates to weight loss and "reduced
OL,17,Fcaloric intake", though more research
OL,18,Fis needed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]wD@JOUwD@`O]xD@\OUyD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
