OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784765892
OL,3,CWeight loss drugs like Mounjaro
OL,4,C'linked to hair loss', researchers say
OL,6,FThey said restricting calories may
OL,7,F"contribute to physiological stress
OL,8,Fand micronutrient deficiencies (for
OL,9,Fexample, iron, zinc, biotin), which
OL,10,Fcan disrupt the hair growth cycle".
OL,12,FOther factors may include the
OL,13,F"metabolic, hormonal, and
OL,14,Fimmunological effects attributed to
OL,15,FGLP-1 receptor agonists that may
OL,16,Finfluence hair follicle growth and
OL,17,Fcycling".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@bO]uD@AOUyD@HO]
